<span id="freeTextContainer6920592193465823467">Deep work at a glance:<br/><br/>✅Periodic isolation —week/days/hours (for reading, thinking, new ideas) [my beautiful Thursdays!]<br/><br/>✅ Quit (or at least strictly manage) social media <br/> <br/>✅ Go online when you have a reason! (Make a list)<br/><br/>✅ 4-hour work/concentration law (+ cheat-hour)<br/><br/>✅ Have a routine [took me about a year(since Jan, 2020)!]<br/><br/>📌 ❓Have a ritual (start + end) <br/><br/>✅ Pomodoro technique<br/><br/>📌 ‼️Have deadlines (shorter than anticipated)<br/><br/>✅ Let others know about your personal routine/isolation<br/> <br/>📌 🦠🚷Combining an activity </span>
  <span id="freeText6920592193465823467" style="display:none">Deep work at a glance:<br /><br />✅Periodic isolation —week/days/hours (for reading, thinking, new ideas) [my beautiful Thursdays!]<br /><br />✅ Quit (or at least strictly manage) social media <br /> <br />✅ Go online when you have a reason! (Make a list)<br /><br />✅ 4-hour work/concentration law (+ cheat-hour)<br /><br />✅ Have a routine [took me about a year(since Jan, 2020)!]<br /><br />📌 ❓Have a ritual (start + end) <br /><br />✅ Pomodoro technique<br /><br />📌 ‼️Have deadlines (shorter than anticipated)<br /><br />✅ Let others know about your personal routine/isolation<br /> <br />📌 🦠🚷Combining an activity which doesn’t need much mental effort (e.g. walking) with analyzing/thinking deeply about a specific problem <br /><br /><br />@Bplus:<br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://castbox.fm/vd/175329715">https://castbox.fm/vd/175329715</a></span>
