          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/25980294-deep-work">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6891202-sisi?shelf=will-not-finish">will-not-finish</a>
