<div id="review_2897561876" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2897561876" />
    <a title="da AL" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/50966750-da-al"><img alt="da AL" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1563928153p2/50966750.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2897561876?book_show_action=true">Jul 15, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="da AL" class="user" itemprop="url" name="da AL" href="/user/show/50966750-da-al">da AL</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audiobook 9781478910008" href="/book/show/30649921-deep-work">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/50966750-da-al?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/50966750-da-al?shelf=audio-books">audio-books</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2897561876" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14073620971669816849">Practical how-to&apos;s as well as researched encouragement to be wary of how much time we give away to anything other than our true passions. By working hard and then playing hard, we can achieve better focus in less time. Audiobook performer Jeff Bottoms reads well.</span>
  <span id="freeText14073620971669816849" style="display:none">Practical how-to's as well as researched encouragement to be wary of how much time we give away to anything other than our true passions. By working hard and then playing hard, we can achieve better focus in less time. Audiobook performer Jeff Bottoms reads well.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14073620971669816849" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


